replies.body:
A very good point, and the very reason why we are seeing Ziggs bot lane is because of his early power. They could implement this the way I've outlined and it may very well change nothing at all.

The promise of EVEN MORE late game power probably isn't something marksmen need. Yet I do like the idea of an adc being able to fork out a few hundred gold for some life steal shots, so he can toggle those on the next time he has to duel with his enemy laner who may have just gotten a lead and bought themselves a {{item:1053}} or {{item:1018}} 

Another factor is that Riot don't like the idea of 'invisible power,' and it's quite possible that even with particle effects to display ammo in use, people would probably still feel cheated by these items winning trades.
